			>
				I build custom web solutions for Creatives & Entrepreneurs.
			</h1>
			<a
				href="/contact"
				class="z-10 ring-2 lg:ring-4 hover:bg-indigo-500 duration-200 ease-linear block mx-auto text-center ring-indigo-500 my-8 mb-16 p-4 lg:p-6 hover:scale-110 w-5/6 lg:w-1/2 rounded-full text-white font-bold text-lg"
				>Let's Chat <Icon class="inline" name={'mdi:arrow-top-right'} /></a
			>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="bg-slate-950 text-white py-8 lg:py-2">
		<div class="flex justify-between items-center p-4 gap-8">
			<img
				class="w-16 lg:w-32 object-cover"
				src="companies/noble-hauling.webp"
			/>
			<img
				class="w-16 lg:w-32 object-cover"
				src="companies/carlton-music.webp"
			/>
			<img class="w-16 lg:w-32 object-cover" src="companies/equature.png" />
			<img
				class="w-16 lg:w-32 object-cover"
				src="companies/withlovecake-logo.png"
			/>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="my-16 text-center mx-1">
		<h2 class="text-xl font-light">When It Comes to Online Presence:</h2>
		<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-700">You Deserve Better.</h3>
		<div>
			<p class="text-left text-sm mx-auto mt-2">
				The digital landscape is constantly evolving, and cookie-cutter
				solutions just donâ€™t cut it anymore. You need more than a websiteâ€”you
				need a dynamic, engaging online presence that truly reflects your brand
				and connects with your audience, and most importantly, drives <i
					class="text-indigo-700">results</i
				>.
			</p>
			<button
				class="z-10 bg-indigo-500 mt-8 p-4 w-5/6 rounded-full text-white font-bold text-lg"
				>Get Results <Icon
					class="inline"
					name={'mdi:arrow-top-right'}
				/></button
			>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="mt-16 text-center p-2 py-8 mb-8">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">
			Elegant Web Solutions for Creative Professionals
		</h2>

		<p class="text-sm text-left mx-auto">
			I specialize in building custom, high-performance websites, applications,
