			real results. Itâ€™s time to level up your online game.
		</p>
	</section>
	<section>
		<h2 class="text-4xl text-center font-bold">What I Build</h2>

		<ServicesHub client:visible />
	</section>
	<section class="my-16">
		<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center">
			Happy Clients are the Best Clients.
		</h1>
		<TestimonialContainer />
	</section>
</RootLayout>
